videos.description: Wake Forest strikes first with a 11-yard touchdown run by Matt Colburn.
videos.headline: Colburn runs it in for Wake TD

videos.description: Jaylen Samuels runs through a huge hole for a score to tie the game.
videos.headline: Samuels sprints in for Wolfpack TD

videos.description: John Wolford finds Tabari Hines on a post for the 21-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Wolford hits Hines for Demon Deacons score

videos.description: Ryan Finley passes to Kelvin Harmon for a 28-yard gain to set the Wolfpack up on the 1-yard line.
videos.headline: N.C. State's Finley drops a dime to Harmon

videos.description: Reggie Gallaspy plunges in from one yard out to tie the game.
videos.headline: Gallaspy runs it in for Wolfpack TD

videos.description: Wake Forest answers as Tabari Hines stretches across the pylon for a 7-yard score.
videos.headline: Hines dives in for Wake TD

videos.description: Emeka Emezie leaps and gets one foot down for the 20-yard Wolfpack touchdown.
videos.headline: N.C. State's Emezie makes nice TD grab

videos.description: John Wolford goes long to Chuck Wade who makes the diving catch for a 41-yard gain.
videos.headline: Wake Forest's Wade lays out for great catch

videos.description: Demetrius Kemp tackles Jaylen Samuels and knocks the ball out to give the ball to Wake Forest.
videos.headline: Wake forces fumble

videos.description: The ball gets tipped twice and Shawn Boone makes a diving catch to give the ball right back to the Wolfpack.
videos.headline: N.C. State makes ridiculous pick

videos.description: John Wolford finds Tabari Hines in the corner of the endzone to give Wake the lead.
videos.headline: Wake Forest's Wolford hits Hines for TD

videos.description: Essang Bassey picks off N.C. State's Hail Mary attempt to seal the upset.
videos.headline: Wake Forest seals win with a pick

videos.description: Clay Matvick and Kirk Morrison break down Wake Forest's upset of N.C. State.
videos.headline: Turnovers key in Wake Forest's upset win
